59.6	Berklee_College_of_Music	Berklee College of Music	Berklee College of Music, located in Boston, Massachusetts, is the largest independent college of contemporary music in the world. Known primarily as a school for jazz, rock and popular music, it also offers college-level courses in a wide range of contemporary and historic styles, including hip hop, reggae, salsa, and bluegrass. To date, 87 Berklee alumni have received 205 Grammy Awards, popular music's highest honor.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/d/dc/Berklee_Seal.png
